<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="upon-prep">upon <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'pɒn/    美 /ə'pɑːn, ə'pɔːn/  </p>
<p>[常与on通用]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在...上面：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He sat upon the grass. 
他坐在草地上。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>对于；关于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like to comment upon your opinion.
我想就你的观点谈谈我的看法。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[与动名词连用] ...之后 (立即)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Upon learning the word “volunteer”, what comes to your mind? 
听到“志愿者”这个词，你会想到什么？</p></div></div>